Revision history for Perl extension ShipIt-Step-Twitter

0.05  Fri Dec 12 19:44:44 CET 2008 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - Changed dist style and Changes back to standard. People didn't like it -
       the nail that sticks out gets hammered down.
     - Added standard test files; this will also help with CPANTS.
     - added default twitter.message
     - added xt/ and moved author tests from t/ there
     - switched to git
     - twitter.distname can also come from META.yml if not given in the config

0.04  Thu, 29 May 2008 12:07:40 -0000 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - set the version to 0.04
     - fixed typo in abstract line
     - updated t/perlcriticrc
     - .shipit: fixed svk.tagpattern

0.03  Mon, 19 Nov 2007 20:50:00 -0000 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - set the version to 0.03
     - new config key 'twitter.distname'
     - more replacement variables: %d = distname, %u = CPAN URL
     - updated .shipit with more descriptive twitter.message
     - added documentation for th new features

0.02  Fri, 16 Nov 2007 14:08:30 -0000 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - set the version to 0.02
     - added explanation of why username and password aren't kept in .shipit
     - Makefile.PL: added auto_install() and process_templates()
     - updated MANIFEST

0.01  Thu, 15 Nov 2007 15:04:38 -0000 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - original version
